column1: Table. Estimates of Evolutionary Divergence between Sequences

The number of base differences per site from between sequences are shown. The analysis involved 121 nucleotide sequences. All ambiguous positions were removed for each sequence pair. There were a total of 43 positions in the final dataset. Evolutionary analyses were conducted in MEGA7 [1].

column3: and Tamura K. (2016). MEGA7: Molecular Evolutionary Genetics Analysis version 7.0 for bigger datasets.Molecular Biology and Evolution 33:1870-1874.
